[
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_809_0",
    "text": "动 充的动是业产的必要条件。对于需要消耗量能源 的业，例如炼铝业等，需布局在能源的供应地。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.3180282250049692,
      0.11232187761944677,
      0.9008149473265752,
      0.15423302598491198
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_809",
    "order": 1
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_809_1",
    "text": "环境条件 不同业对环境条件有着不同的要求。如酿酒业需要优 质的源，电业需要清洁的环境等。有些企业在产过程中， 会造成污染、污染和固体废弃物污染等，影响类的产和 活，因此业布局也要考虑对环境的影响。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.3164380838799443,
      0.16876222408493993,
      0.9000198767640628,
      0.2598491198658843
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_809",
    "order": 2
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_809_2",
    "text": "思考",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.20512820512820512,
      0.27270187203129365,
